OL,4,G2100FCountdown to War
OL,5,     GOn 1st September 1939, 1.5
OL,6,     Gmillion German soldiers poured
OL,7,     Ginto Poland, beginning the
OL,8,     Gcountdown to the 2nd World War.
OL,9,     GJJ Chalmers and Raksha Dave tell
OL,10,     Gthe dramatic story.
OL,11,G2200FCountdown to War
OL,12,     GJJ Chalmers and Raksha Dave
OL,13,     Gexplore 2nd September 1939, as
OL,14,     GGermany's invasion of Poland
OL,15,     Gescalates. RAF recruits deploy,
OL,16,     GLondon hospitals are emptied and
OL,17,     GParliament braces for war.
